A '''vapor sampler''' was a piece of equipment used in demolitions work, particularly to detect hidden explosives. It worked by sampling the air that it was passed through, analyzing it for trace elements left behind by certain chemical compounds that were used to create [[Bomb/Legends|bombs]]. [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] used a vapor sampler when searching for [[core bomb]]s while aboard the ''[[Aurorient Express]]'' in [[38 BBY/Legends|38 BBY]].

